extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
A Rift Torn Betwenn Worlds!

The hour grown desperate, and two stand at the brink! The Pokémn TCG: XY-BREAKpoint expansion reveals the growing rift between the twin world, first discovered by Shiny Gyrados-EX. As the rift tears through the skies, more Pokémon are drawn into the struggle, including Greninja BREAK, luxray BREAK, and Mega Scizor-EX! Can they mend the rift and save both worlds from collision chaos?

Each XY BREAKpoint Sleeved Booster Pack contains 10 random cards.

Cards vary by pack. Booster packs may vary by product.
